The 'Walking Simulator' tag on SteamDB lists games that offer immersive, first-person experiences focused primarily on exploration and movement. These games typically prioritize narrative and atmosphere over traditional gameplay elements such as combat or puzzles. Players assume the role of a character navigating various environments, interacting with objects, and discovering the stories and secrets hidden within. The genre has gained popularity for its ability to evoke emotion and provide a sense of immersion that can be both relaxing and thought-provoking.
